folder: York Street & St. John's Lane, Manhattan, NY
original_title: Manhattan: York Street - St. John's Lane
text:
2 York Street, at the S.E. corner of St. John's Lane. Also shown is St. John's Lane, east side, south from and including York to, but not including Beach Streets. Building concerned is a 3-story frame house.

December 7, 1927.

P. L. Sperr.
